fields.primaryText: Pulls hair, ear, body parts of others
Attacks or pokes others with weapon (blade, stick, pencil)
Tears / pulls threads from own or other clothing
Tears up own or others books, papers, magzines
Interrupts in between when others are talking
Makes loud noise when others are working or reading
Takes others possession without their permission openly
Tells others what to do and wants his/her way (bossy)
Puts objects into eyes / noses / ear
Snakes parts of the body repeatedly
Hoards unwanted objects ( sticks, thread, pieces of old clothes)
Play with unwanted objects like chappal, strings, faces and dirt excessively
Kisses, hugs, and licks people unnecsssarily
Does not sit at one place for required time
Does not pay attention to what is told
Does not continue with the task at hand for required time
Does opposite of what is required
Takes very long time intentionally to complete a task
Lies or twists the truth to his own advantage of blames others
Cheats in games or no sense of fair play
Makes sexual advances towards members of opposite sex
Touches own private parts in public
Touches others private parts in public
